      <li><strong>Toll Free:</strong> 866-810-9441</li>
      <li><strong>Fax:</strong> 218-776-3507 Toll Free</li>
      <li><strong>Fax:</strong> 866-810-7008</li>
      <li><strong>Office Hours:</strong> Monday – Friday 8:00 am – 5:00 pm</li>
      <li><strong>Email:</strong> info@livingspringservices.com</li>
